Endaa natopolosakaki nkitanyaanyukot


1  Oo taa endaa napolosakini nkitanyaanyukot naaitaai nkaitin. aikiyiolo doi anaa enoshi nijojo, “aikiata pooki eng'eno.” Kake ore ina “ng'eno” inyi naa olwuasa epik iltung'ana; kake keshetu ninye enyorrata ltung'ana. 
2  Te nejo likae keeta ae nayiolo nemeeta ilo enayiolo anaa enaaishiaakino neyiolo; 
3  kake ore ake olonyor Enkai neyiolo Enkai ninye.


4  Ore te nkinosata e ina daa napolosakini enkitanyaanyukoto naitaai enkai “neme toki te nkop,” nikiyiolo aajo, “meetae ae Ai neme nabo ake.” 
5  Naa te neetae nena naaji nkaitin, te keper aashu te nkop, amu esipa eetae nkaitin kumok, o laitoriak kumok, 
6  kake ore te iyiook nabo ake Enkai, Papa, laa ninye eing'uaa ntokitin pooki, naa ninye kinchuyie iyiook naa obo Olaitoriani, Yesu Kristo laa ninye eimu ntokitin pooki naa ninye kinchuyie. 
7  Kake eeta ake pooki ng'ae eng'eno enye. Ore amu etamoo kulikae tung'ana nena kitaanyaanyukot naaitaai nkaitin, neton edol lelo endaa nanya etiu anaa enatopolosakaki ina kitanyaanyukoto; ore to ltau, lenye enkaraki naton eshal neidurukie ina. 
8  Meisho iyiook endaa errepet te Nkai; nimikilau toki te neitu kinya endaa, nemeeta ae nikitum ti nikinya. 
9  Entodol naa ake ate meaku ina naishoro intae narror lelo ooshal. 
10  Te nedol intae oltung'ani oshal, intae taa lelo ng'eni, itonini aadaa te mesa e nkaji nasayieki enkitanyaanyukoto, ijo meitagol ina oltau, te ina shalan enye, nelo ninye anya endaa natopolosakaki nena kitanyaanyukot? 
11  Neaku ina ng'eno inyi natara ilo tung'ani oshal, ilo alashe otua Kristo te nkaraki ninye. 
12  Ore pee intaasiasa ilalashera linyi ng'ok naaikununo neijia, iltauja lenye itipika lbaa, niyiololo eshal, Kristo intaasa nena ng'ok. 
13  Neaku te naa kendaa narror olalashe lai, nemaitoki ai kata anya nkiri, pee marror olalashe lai.

